import math

def update_weights(x1, x2, y, w1, w2):
    z = w1 * x1 - w2 * x2
    y_pred = 1 / (1 + math.exp(-z))
    e = y - y_pred
    dw1 = e * y_pred * (1 - y_pred) * x1
    dw2 = e * y_pred * (1 - y_pred) * x2
    return (w1 + dw1, w2 + dw2)
